{
  "stem": "20978.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I hired local people to open up the grave.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I went to the tar carpenter and paid him, and-- and-- and paid the midwife for being-- and thanked them for helping us, for being nice.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And-- and nobody would go down into the grave to put the rope under.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Of course, I went down.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I put the rope under the box.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we picked her up and there was a doctor there, had to open the coffin.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I couldn't avoid it, to look.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And that's what I live with the rest of my life.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We took her back to-- I took her to Szombathely, where we had a-- a regular levaya, what a Jewish woman deserves.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And that's where she's resting.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I've been back, in the past 50 years, three times.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They gave it to us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I hope to go again next year.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] As a matter of fact, I have a nephew, my sister's son, who is 35 years old.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "[DRINKS] Lives in California.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "He-- he travels to Europe.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And when I-- when his mother, I guess, told him the story, and I told him some of it, he wanted to go to see the grave.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And he went to Europe two years ago, and went to this town, the city, Szombathely, an American boy that don't speak English-- I mean, don't speak Hungarian.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "The cemetery was closed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And he climbed over a wall.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Took him an hour.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "He found the grave.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "He wanted to spend a little time with his grandmother, that he never had.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "[CRYING] And I helped take my two daughters next year, to their grandmother's grave that they never knew.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
